TI Chronically ill children.  A psychologically and emotionally deviant
   population?.
SO J-Abnorm-Child-Psychol. 1976. 4(2). P 99-110.
MJ ADAPTATION-PSYCHOLOGICAL.  CHRONIC-DISEASE.  SOCIAL-ADJUSTMENT.
MN ACHIEVEMENT.  ADOLESCENCE.  ADULT.  ASTHMA: co.
   CHILD-BEHAVIOR-DISORDERS: co.  CHILD.  CHILD-PRESCHOOL.
   CYSTIC-FIBROSIS: co.  DEFENSE-MECHANISMS.  DEPENDENCY-PSYCHOLOGY.
   DIABETES-MELLITUS-INSULIN-DEPENDENT: co.  FEMALE.
   HEARING-DISORDERS:  co.  HUMAN.  INTERNAL-EXTERNAL-CONTROL.  MALE.
